@startuml sq_wrl01_append_event
' ============================================================
' Title:     WRL-01 — APPEND Event to Wire Log
' Boundary:  nasim code agent CLI
' Purpose:   Append event to wire log
' Milestone: v1.0
' Version:   1.0.0
' Source:    docs/audit/audit.2026.06.20.deep.domain.audit.md
' Review:    —
' ============================================================

actor "Developer" as user

box "Agent Layer" #E3F2FD
  participant "AgentOrchestrator" as agent
end box
box "Wire Log Layer" #FFF3E0
  participant "WireLogger" as logger
  participant "EventSerializer" as serializer
end box
box "FileSystem Layer" #F3E5F5
  participant "FileSystem" as fs
end box

note over user, fs
  Scope:
    - wrl01 APPEND Event — append event to wire log

  Preconditions:
    - Wire log file path configured
    - FileSystem write access available

  Contexts:
    - Called on every significant agent event
    - Prerequisite for WRL-02 (Read Log), WRL-03 (Fork), WRL-04 (Replay)

  Excludes:
    - Log reading (handled by WRL-02)
    - Session forking (handled by WRL-03)

  Rollback:
    - Write failure → event lost, log warning

  Design:
    - WireLogger appends serialized events to log file
    - EventSerializer handles JSON serialization with timestamps
    - Each event includes: type, timestamp, payload, session_id
    - Log is append-only (no in-place edits)
    - Buffered writes for performance (flush on session end)

  Returns:
    - Success: AppendResult with event_id and offset
    - Failure: AppendError with details
end note

== wrl01 APPEND Event ==

agent -> logger : APPEND_EVENT(event)
activate logger

logger -> serializer : serialize(event)
activate serializer
serializer --> logger : serialized_event
deactivate serializer

logger -> logger : add_metadata(serialized_event, session_id, timestamp)

logger -> fs : append_file(log_path, serialized_event)
activate fs
fs --> logger : write_result
deactivate fs

logger --> agent : AppendResult(event_id, offset)
deactivate logger

note over user, fs
  Flow:
    - AgentOrchestrator → WireLogger → EventSerializer + FileSystem → AppendResult

  State:
    - IDLE → SERIALIZING → APPENDING → DONE

  Failure:
    - Write failure → event lost, warning logged

  Success:
    - AppendResult with event_id and offset

  Key invariants:
    - Log is append-only
    - Each event has unique event_id
    - Timestamp always included
end note

@enduml
